<h2 id="smart-goals">SMART Goals</h2>

<p>Okay, weâ€™re going to talk about SMART goals. SMART is, unfortunately, <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/SMART_criteria">an acronym</a>. Iâ€™m not a big fan of these sort of business-speak, feel-good, personal-development-y things, but this one Iâ€™ve made an exception for. Simply put, SMART goals are:</p>

<p>Specific
